---
/**
 * /careers — employment / hiring page.
 *
 * Replaces the legacy /join-our-team/ page (slug cleanup per
 * launch-checklist.md — 301 from /join-our-team/ → /careers/ at launch).
 *
 * Live twistedpin.com/join-our-team/ application flow:
 *   - "Why is it worth working with us?" — 4-icon benefits row:
 *     Fun Work Environment / Health Insurance / Dental & Vision /
 *     Company Sponsored 401k (per user 2026-05-05 screenshots)
 *   - "Are You Ready to Join Our Team?" CTA → external application:
 *     https://www.employment-application.net/application.php?application=84
 *
 * 2026-05-05 update: page rebuilt against the real benefits + real
 * application link. Replaces the "email contactus@twistedpin.com"
 * placeholder flow that was here from the initial tier-2 batch.
 *
 * Voice register: confident, direct. The brand is adults-first /
 * sharper than most hospitality, and hiring copy should match.
 * Don't overclaim culture ("amazing team", "family vibes"). Don't
 * say "fun work environment" verbatim — that's tonal opposite of
 * voice.md (try-hard hype). The fact (welcoming workplace) is real;
 * convey it in voice ("a venue you'd actually want to be in after
 * your shift ends"). Specifics > adjectives applies — name the
 * benefits factually.
 *
 * TODOs (non-blocking):
 *   - Open positions list — pending ops if specific roles. The
 *     external application form (employment-application.net) seems
 *     to handle role selection itself.
 *   - Service area in title/description matches live site
 *     (Plainfield, Naperville, Bolingbrook) for SEO continuity.
 *   - Staff photo shipped 2026-05-07 — careers-team-* (DSC_0289 from
 *     Pics Social Media). Editorial section between "What You Get"
 *     and "How to Apply" pairs the team shot with the "Best of Will
 *     County 2025" award framing, doubling as social proof + award
 *     credibility marker before the conversion ask.
 */
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import SnapFooter from "../components/snap/SnapFooter.astro";
---
<Base
  title="Careers — Twisted Pin Plainfield IL"
  description="Hiring for bartenders, servers, kitchen, and front-of-house at Twisted Pin in Plainfield, IL. Serving Naperville, Bolingbrook, and the surrounding area."
>

  <section class="t2-hero" data-hero aria-labelledby="careers-h1">
    <div class="t2-hero-copy">
      <p class="t-eyebrow hero-fade" data-delay-ms="0">Employment</p>
      <h1 class="t-display t2-hero-headline hero-fade" id="careers-h1" data-delay-ms="120">
        Work here.
      </h1>
      <p class="t2-hero-sub hero-fade" data-delay-ms="320">
        Bartenders, servers, kitchen, front desk. If you're good at
        what you do and want to do it somewhere that takes the work
        seriously, we want to hear from you.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="t2-section" aria-labelledby="careers-perks-h2">
    <div class="t2-section-inner">
      <h2 class="t-eyebrow" id="careers-perks-h2" style="font-size:11px;">What You Get</h2>
      <p class="t2-section-body">
        The basics, sorted:
      </p>
      <ul class="t2-list">
        <li>Health Insurance Offerings</li>
        <li>Dental + vision</li>
        <li>401k, company-sponsored</li>
        <li>A venue you'd actually want to be in after your shift ends</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Social proof — staff team + Best of Will County 2025 award.
      Editorial break between perks and the application CTA. */}
  <section class="t2-section careers-team-section" aria-labelledby="careers-team-h2">
    <div class="t2-section-inner">
      <div class="careers-team-frame">
        <picture>
          <source type="image/avif" srcset="/snap/careers-team-540.avif 540w, /snap/careers-team-900.avif 900w" sizes="(min-width: 1025px) 480px, 90vw" />
          <source type="image/webp" srcset="/snap/careers-team-540.webp 540w, /snap/careers-team-900.webp 900w" sizes="(min-width: 1025px) 480px, 90vw" />
          <img
            class="careers-team-img"
            src="/snap/careers-team-540.jpg"
            srcset="/snap/careers-team-540.jpg 540w, /snap/careers-team-900.jpg 900w"
            sizes="(min-width: 1025px) 480px, 90vw"
            alt="The Twisted Pin staff team holding the Best of Will County 2025 Bowling Alley award in front of the GUTTERS HAPPEN BEER HELPS sign"
            width="540"
            height="960"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />
        </picture>
      </div>
      <h2 class="t-eyebrow" id="careers-team-h2" style="font-size:11px;">Best of Will County 2025</h2>
      <p class="t2-section-body">
        Voted Best Bowling Alley in Will County by Herald-News readers.
        The team holding the plaque is who you'd be on shift with.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="t2-section" aria-labelledby="careers-apply-h2">
    <div class="t2-section-inner">
      <h2 class="t-eyebrow" id="careers-apply-h2" style="font-size:11px;">How to Apply</h2>
      <p class="t2-section-body">
        Fill out the application below — we keep it open year-round
        across bar, kitchen, lanes, arcade, and front-of-house.
        Weekend availability is a real plus; Friday and Saturday are
        when the room comes alive.
      </p>

      <a class="btn btn-solid" href="https://www.employment-application.net/application.php?application=84" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        Fill out application
      </a>

      <p class="t2-section-body" style="margin-top: 28px;">
        Twisted Pin is in Plainfield, IL — easy commute from Naperville,
        Bolingbrook, Romeoville, Shorewood, Joliet, and Oswego.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <SnapFooter />
</Base>

<style>
  /* Staff-team editorial frame — portrait photo, constrained max-width
     so the section reads as an editorial accent, not a hero takeover.
     aspect-ratio kept at the source's native 9:16 so the team + award
     fit without a tight crop. */
  .careers-team-frame {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: var(--radius-surface);
    aspect-ratio: 9 / 16;
    max-width: 360px;
    margin: 0 auto 28px;
  }
  @media (min-width: 1025px) {
    .careers-team-frame { max-width: 420px; }
  }
  .careers-team-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center;
  }
  /* Section copy is centered on tier-2 pages (matches sibling .t2-section)
     so the eyebrow + body align under the photo. */
  .careers-team-section .t2-section-inner {
    text-align: center;
  }
</style>
